# parity ledger: interactive isEnabled excludes noninteractive
# parity ledger: interactive load path
# parity ledger: noninteractive descriptor type
# parity ledger: noninteractive support flag
# parity ledger: noninteractive isEnabled requires noninteractive
# parity ledger: noninteractive hidden getter mirrors session state
